# AquaFlow environment variables (Vite exposes only VITE_-prefixed vars to the client)
#
# Track A (LIVE) sources are declared in ./data-sources.config.json. Real
# endpoints/keys are TODO(paint). Secrets live here as VITE_-prefixed vars — a
# client SPA cannot commit keys. International sources (Open-Meteo/WorldTides)
# are ALWAYS labeled "สำรอง" (backup) and never drive a decision on their own.

# Optional — WorldTides API key (https://www.worldtides.info). Used only as a
# labeled international BACKUP for the tide source. If unset, the app tries the
# keyless Open-Meteo Marine endpoint (also backup) and otherwise falls back to a
# modeled sine tide, clearly labeled "จำลอง" in the UI.
VITE_WORLDTIDES_KEY=
